titleStmt.sponsor: Medieval Latin Manuscripts in the National Library: Cataloguing and Digitization

publicationStmt.publisher: Manuscripta.se: A Digital Catalogue of Manuscripts in Sweden

msDesc.head: Legislative texts for the Birgittine order: Regula Salvatoris. Petrus Olavi, Additiones ad regulam Salvatoris. Declaraciones dominorum. Liber usuum

supportDesc.foliation: Foliation 1-89 by modern hand in pencil takes account of the two flyleaves. Contemporary foliation in the top margin 1-78 (ff. 12r-88v).

p.note: On the inside of the left cover is noted in a modern hand: "A 11. Regula S. Salvatoris in prima Persona" and in a medieval hand: "Hiis diebus confessor ministrabit sororibus corpus Christi" followed by a list of days.
Annotation referring to the contents of the volume on the upper pastedown by contemporary scribe.
Prayers. Incipit: [R]epelle a nobis. Explicit: ...abstineat remedium perenne

decoDesc.p: 3-5 line initials, mainly red, several with reserved lines, some with pen-drawn decoration; 2- or 3-line red initials, mainly plain but some also with reserved lines; capitals touched with red.

binding.p: Leather binding over wooden boards. Metal clasp attached to the fore-edge. Two bosses of bone (traces of a third) on the back cover.

history.origin:
Vadstena monastery.
Sweden ,15th century, second half
history.provenance: Antikvitetsarkivet, listed in U 90:2, 8v, as no. 93 (written in brown ink on the left cover inside) and in U 90:4, p. 44, as no. 95. Listed in Berch’s catalogue 1758 with the shelfmark A 11 (current signum). Notes by a 16th century hand on the pastedown of the right cover inside. On the spine "95" in brown ink, at the top of the spine the letters "EE".
history.acquisition: To the National Library from Antikvitetsarkivet.

msItem.title: Alphabetical index
msItem.rubric: Legem statuit ei in via quam elegit Elegimus namque non tamen latam viam mandatorum dei ymmo artam semitam consiliorum que ergo nobis statuta est in legem seruandam ad salutem Hec via et semita electa continentur in regula sancti saluatoris, et Augustini, addicionibus prioris, declaracionibus doctorum, libro vsuum, et actis capituli hec omnia in tabula
msItem.incipit: Abbatissa eligatur et sit caput et domina omnium
msItem.explicit: Christus Ihesus est dator regule sancte huius ordinisque fundator 1 b c Ipse enim est principium et finis alpha et o deus et homo ipsi honor et gloria in seculis
msItem.note: The index refers to the contemporary foliation and paragraphs in the manuscript.

msItem.title: Regula Salvatoris (The Birgittine Rule, the first person version)
msItem.rubric: Regula sancti saluatoris in prima persona. Narratur hic modus qualiter domina Birgitta habebat reuelaciones diuinas (...) Capitulum 1 prologi

msItem.title: The Rule of St Augustine
msItem.incipit: Ante omnia fratres karissimi diligatur deus deinde proximus
msItem.explicit: ut ei debitum dimittatur et in temptacionem ne inducatur Amen.

msItem.title: Petrus Olavi, Addiciones
msItem.rubric: Incipiunt addiciones domini prioris petri ad regulam saluatoris Et primo de gradibus seu signis vere dilectionis. Capitulum primum
msItem.incipit: Humilitas vera est timere deum omni hora non amare propriam voluntatem
msItem.explicit: Sorores sepeliantur in ambitibus et in ecclesia infra crates Et similiter fratres. Amen

msItem.title: Excerpts from St. Birgitta, Revelaciones Extravagantes
msItem.rubric: Sequuntur reuelaciones pertinentes ad statuta Et primo de organis non habendis
msItem.incipit: Christus loquitur filii Israel quia carnales erant multa

msItem.title: Rules for deacons and subdeacons in the Birgittine Order
msItem.rubric: Dyaconus et subdyaconus sic ministrabunt induti ad missas
msItem.incipit: Dyaconi ministrabunt vicissim ad altaria secundum ordinem suum
msItem.explicit: Item dyaconus thurificabit omnem inhabitacionem fratrum in vigilia natiuitatis Christi et vigilia epyphanie domini finitis vesperis

msItem.title: Constitucio Vadstenensis
msItem.rubric: Hec est constitucio Watzstenensis qualiter diuinum officium et festa seu solemnitates debent obseruari in monasterio
msItem.incipit: Sicut regula sancti saluatoris precipit fratres clerici
msItem.explicit: ...vt in illo legat vel studeat sub horis vel in missa. Amen.

msItem.title: Declaraciones dominorum
msItem.rubric: Declaraciones dominorum de Nuceria cardinalis Vrbeuetani alfonsi et aliorum vt infra patet. de roma misse
msItem.incipit: Hic continentur declaraciones dubiorum missorum de monasterio sancte Marie in Vastzenom
msItem.explicit: Videtur quod cum consilio sui proprii confessoris ipse enim diligencius examinauerat consciencias earum Amen
msItem.finalRubric: Expliciunt declaraciones dominorum prius positorum super regulam sancti saluatoris

msItem.title: Liber usuum (The Customary of the Vadstena Brothers)
msItem.rubric: Ihesu Christi nomine inuocato humiliter et deuote Incipit prologus in librum vsuum fratrum monasterii sancte marie virginis et birgitte in Vatzstenom
msItem.incipit: Quoniam exemplo primitiue ecclesie congregacionisque fidelium
msItem.explicit: vt notatur super verbo nigrorum supra et secundum Iohannem andree

msItem.title: Confirmation of the decisions made at the Birgittine general chapter in Gnadenberg 1487
msItem.incipit: Vilhelmus dei gracia Eystetensis alias Aureatensis ecclesie Episcopus Sacrosancte Maguntinensis sedis Cancellarius
msItem.explicit: signavi rogatus et requisitus in fidem et testimonium omnium et singulorum premissorum.
